---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout>
	<h1>Derks Financial QBO Internal Tool</h1>
	<p>
		An internal application operated by Derks Financial for managing the
		company's QuickBooks Online accounts and related business workflows. Not
		intended for public sale, resale, or use by unrelated third parties.
	</p>

	<h2 id="connect">Connect or reconnect</h2>
	<p>
		To connect or reconnect a QuickBooks Online company to the application,
		an authorized administrator signs in to QuickBooks Online, runs the
		application's built-in connection workflow, and approves the requested
		permissions on the Intuit consent screen.
	</p>

	<h2 id="disconnect">Disconnect</h2>
	<p>
		A QuickBooks Online company can be disconnected at any time either from
		inside the application (which revokes the refresh token with Intuit and
		removes locally stored credentials) or from inside QuickBooks Online via
		<em>Apps → Connected Apps → Disconnect</em>.
	</p>

	<h2>Legal</h2>
	<ul>
		<li><a href="/derks-intuit-developer-app-details/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
		<li><a href="/derks-intuit-developer-app-details/license">End User License Agreement</a></li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Contact</h2>
	<p>
		Derks Financial<br />
